Text.Value: What were you doing in the village?
What were you doing in the barn?
*The corpse seems willing to speak - but not to its killer.*

EditorData.SFXTags: 'the corpse grimaced and tured away' foley

Text.Value: *The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*
Were you and Grukkoh in love?
Grukkoh... baby boy... we take a break... together...
From... crash... took by... bad people...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*
What weapon were you looking for?

Synopsis: Butthir the ogre has been killed - you are now speaking with her corpse.
